    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "Long \"klack\" with good top-rope opportunities. Climbing has been taking place here since the 1980s. The Uppland Trail runs close to the car park and leads down to the bathing area at Tenasjön (1km). In some winters, climbable ice forms on the lower slab sections.",
