          "body": {
            "text": "A long \"klack\" with good top-rope opportunities. Climbing has been practiced here since the 80s. The Uppland Trail passes near the parking lot and leads down to Tenasjön's swimming area (1km). In some winters, climbable ice forms on the lower slab areas.",
